OL,3,CJersey's plan to ban new fossil fuel
OL,4,Cboilers pushed back indefinitely
OL,6,F"I recognise that pushing back the
OL,7,Flegislation date may have an impact on
OL,8,Four emission reductions and I have
OL,9,Fasked officers to consider how we can
OL,10,Fincrease the voluntary switch to low
OL,11,Fcarbon heating systems to compensate
OL,12,Ffor this."
OL,14,FDeputy Luce added that the Government
OL,15,Fwill instead focus on technical
OL,16,Fguidance and reviewing building
OL,17,Fbylaws, the construction standards
OL,18,Fthose across the island are held to,
OL,19,Fto work out what is needed to support
OL,20,Fthe net-zero target.
