OL,3,CJersey's plan to ban new fossil fuel
OL,4,Cboilers pushed back indefinitely
OL,6,FHomes that are sold or rented out were
OL,7,Fdue to be forced by law to have a
OL,8,Fmandatory certificate to show energy
OL,9,Fefficiency and emissions but this has
OL,10,Falso been delayed until after the next
OL,11,Felection in 2026.
OL,13,FPeople wishing to install electric
OL,14,Fboilers in Guernsey have been facing
OL,15,Ftheir own challenges .
OL,17,FA lack of capacity in the electricity
OL,18,Fsystem has left some on a waiting list
OL,19,Fwith Guernsey Electricity saying it is
OL,20,Fworking on upgrading its network.
